Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.78,0:00:06.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Count Sebring. Count Raffia. Count Orga.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.16,0:00:11.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you all for allowing me to\Nintrude on your valuable time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.25,0:00:14.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I am sorry for your loss,\NCount Troyard.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.33,0:00:16.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What happened to Count Saazbaum\Nis most regrettable.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.88,0:00:21.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When he was alive, my father was\Ngreatly indebted to him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.38,0:00:24.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If it is in my power, whatever assistance\Nyou may request is yours.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.51,0:00:26.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, that is most kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.06,0:00:31.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,However, now is not the time to wallow\Nin individual sentimentality.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.18,0:00:33.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Most commendable.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.60,0:00:36.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is the time for the Orbital\NKnights to band together{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.73,0:00:39.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and press forward with\Nthe invasion of Earth.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.23,0:00:43.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That is the best way\Nto honor Count Saazbaum.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.36,0:00:48.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed. Our ships must sail forward\Ntogether towards the same goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.41,0:00:50.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ah, now I see.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.04,0:00:53.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You intend to take\Nthe helm, then?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.50,0:00:57.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I may be so presumptuous.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.17,0:01:03.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}By the way... I understand that\Nyou are to duel Count Marylcian?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.55,0:01:07.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I find it odd to be fighting\Nwhen we must band together.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.22,0:01:09.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't you agree, Count Troyard?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.93,0:01:14.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No lowly Terran...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.85,0:01:18.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No lowly Terran could possibly\Nbe a match for mighty Vers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.65,0:01:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Such an assumption\Ncreates an opening.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.64,0:01:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Which becomes a tear.\NAnd then an enormous hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.57,0:01:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And then it disintegrates completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.53,0:01:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That is the current state\Nof the Orbital Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.29,0:01:33.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You go too far, Count Troyard!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.58,0:01:37.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As you are aware,\NI am not Vers-born.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.42,0:01:41.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,However, being an outsider\Naffords me a certain perspective.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.63,0:01:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This upcoming duel is also the result\Nof an Orbital Knight's hubris.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.30,0:01:48.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I believe it to be my responsibility\Nto teach him the error of his ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.64,0:01:51.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I see. You have a point.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.85,0:01:53.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Count Orga!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.68,0:01:58.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I am loathe to admit it.\NNevertheless, it is the truth.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.52,0:02:01.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Some portion of it, at least.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.32,0:02:05.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I shall leave the matter to\Nyour discretion, Count Troyard.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.70,0:02:10.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Your attack on Trident Base\Nwas magnificent.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.74,0:02:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Count Sebring, Count Raffia.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.00,0:02:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for doing me the honor of\Nlistening to my many rude remarks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.73,0:04:04.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All cruise missiles appear\Nto have been intercepted.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.02,0:04:06.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like a saturation attack\Nisn't gonna work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.57,0:04:10.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Count Selnakis' Kataphrakt, Scorching Solis.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.99,0:04:15.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The firing range of its onboard beam weapon\Nextends out to the Satellite Belt,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.41,0:04:17.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,making air support\Nimpossible, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.66,0:04:19.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's quite the monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.83,0:04:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Message from assault team.\NThey're about to make landfall.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.50,0:04:27.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Launch cruise missiles.\NKeep his attention on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.80,0:04:33.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Getting up close and personal\Nis the only way, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.26,0:04:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saddle up, people!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.80,0:04:38.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Get ready to launch, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.24,0:04:56.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Inko? Inko!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.49,0:04:58.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.03,0:04:58.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.91,0:05:01.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing. Say, Rayet...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.75,0:05:02.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.87,0:05:08.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There was that manhunt all of a sudden\Nthe other day. For um, Ma... Mazoo...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.46,0:05:09.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Count Mazuurek?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.96,0:05:11.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right, him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.21,0:05:13.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How do you suppose he escaped?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.43,0:05:14.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Beats me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.63,0:05:17.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Inaho knows anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.01,0:05:18.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.18,0:05:21.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he went to interrogate him.\NDid you hear anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.85,0:05:23.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.52,0:05:26.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.02,0:05:27.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Time to launch. Let's go.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.98,0:05:29.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.94,0:05:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Inko.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.58,0:05:41.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To think that such a simple mechanism\Ncan indicate one's bearings...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.95,0:05:45.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Such a device would only work on\Na planet with a magnetic field.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.62,0:05:49.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then... Count Troyard\Nand Inaho Kaizuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.96,0:05:54.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Both are sons of Earth.\NCan they be trusted?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.05,0:06:00.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So simple, one cannot\Ngo astray, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.85,0:06:04.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,True of many things, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.15,0:06:11.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really going to\Nfight the duel, Slaine?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.65,0:06:15.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I have been challenged,\Nso I cannot back down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.78,0:06:21.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This happened because I allowed\NCount Marylcian's visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.03,0:06:24.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all. It is thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.21,0:06:28.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It is the perfect opportunity\Nto demonstrate my strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.88,0:06:30.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I am victorious in this duel,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.79,0:06:34.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,it will act as a deterrent against\NOrbital Knights who oppose me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.09,0:06:37.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There is nothing to be\Nconcerned about.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.14,0:06:44.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your dream might actually\Ncome true one day, won't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.35,0:06:46.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have no dream to...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.27,0:06:50.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A Terran who had been held in contempt\Nnow holds genuine power within Vers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.61,0:06:55.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have felt it ever since\Nwe first met.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.32,0:06:58.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That you and I were kindred spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.78,0:07:03.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you intend to hold on to your grudge\Nagainst the royal family forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.12,0:07:04.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.24,0:07:10.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's incredibly satisfying to see someone without\Na drop of Versian blood in him gaining power.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.92,0:07:14.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think you will never\Nlet go, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.59,0:07:16.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of your princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.26,0:07:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You genuinely love her, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.14,0:07:25.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I may...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.02,0:07:28.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Would you let me help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.73,0:07:32.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.48,0:07:35.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,if I am only my sister's substitute.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.74,0:07:39.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All platoons, report in!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.49,0:07:41.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Belgian Platoon, in position!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.36,0:07:43.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Maremmano Platoon, in position!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.41,0:07:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pottok Platoon, in position!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.20,0:07:46.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lokai Platoon, in position!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.95,0:07:48.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mustang Platoon, in position!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.96,0:07:51.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way to evade that\Nbastard's beam weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.92,0:07:54.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Assume you're history\Nif you're spotted.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.17,0:07:55.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Begin operation!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.98,0:08:16.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A smoke screen that scatters everything\Nfrom infrared to radar waves, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.32,0:08:17.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Clever monkeys.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.57,0:08:21.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.95,0:08:23.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.75,0:08:35.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Clydesdale Leader to all platoons!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.59,0:08:38.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Deploy on the south bank\Nand keep that smoke up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.76,0:08:41.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You waste your time...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.22,0:08:44.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fire, fire, fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.68,0:08:47.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Keep his attention on us!\NDon't get hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.93,0:08:51.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How are we supposed to get\Nhis attention and not get hit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.64,0:08:53.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Nao?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.28,0:09:02.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Up you go. Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.21,0:09:13.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rayet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.12,0:09:15.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Okay, I'm patching you in!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.54,0:09:20.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Acoustic analysis.\NEnemy coordinates pinpointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.51,0:09:26.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Target is at 29.951103, -90.085579.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.72,0:09:29.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Roger that. Targeting location.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.22,0:09:31.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Fire.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.22,0:09:32.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Firing, roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.77,0:09:38.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Counting down. Five, four, three, two,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.19,0:09:39.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.98,0:09:42.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.69,0:09:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Impact. Correct 037, 025.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.12,0:09:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It came from the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.20,0:09:50.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.62,0:09:56.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ship cannon fire, eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.88,0:10:02.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Missed us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.67,0:10:06.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A beam weapon can only fire\Nin a straight line.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.51,0:10:08.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If we hide behind the curve of\Nthe Earth, it can't hit us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.89,0:10:14.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But since our shells follow a parabola\Ndue to the Earth's gravity,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.34,0:10:16.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,they can reach\Nover the horizon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.22,0:10:18.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As long as it's possible\Nto target the thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.90,0:10:22.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Correct 283, -472.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.32,0:10:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ultra high speed rounds, fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.41,0:10:32.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Curse them, how are they\Ntargeting me so accurately
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.16,0:10:34.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,without observation satellites?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.50,0:10:36.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.71,0:10:45.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The UAVs that were relaying our\Nlaser comms have been taken out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.51,0:10:48.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We can't get through\Nto Ensign Kaizuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.13,0:10:49.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rayet!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.59,0:10:52.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go to tracer rounds.\NFire exactly as I say!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.73,0:10:58.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Over there, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.73,0:11:01.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nao!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.94,0:11:03.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.48,0:11:05.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tracer rounds, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.15,0:11:08.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you seriously think you can bring\Ndown my Solis from that far?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.95,0:11:11.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki, get clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.08,0:11:15.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Warrant Officer Kaizuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.16,0:11:16.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.20,0:11:17.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.25,0:11:20.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Second volley! And a third!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.46,0:11:23.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Correct 002, 003! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.84,0:11:25.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kaizuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.59,0:11:26.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.76,0:11:29.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stand right there and\Nmonologue at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.93,0:11:33.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Be reduced to ash\Nby my scorching light!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.76,0:11:36.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead and shoot,\Nyou frog-faced bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.61,0:11:49.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yuki!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.11,0:11:54.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm okay. I just lost an arm.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.03,0:11:55.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How about you guys?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.12,0:11:58.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're fine. Ensign Kaizuka is safe, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.37,0:12:00.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's great news...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.42,0:12:02.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, it's not.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.42,0:12:06.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to get clear. You disobeyed\Nan order, Warrant Officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.71,0:12:10.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, don't talk like you're superior to me\Njust because you're a higher rank.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.38,0:12:12.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am your superior.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.34,0:12:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No little brother can order\Nhis big sister around.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.93,0:12:21.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Clydesdale Leader to all units.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.35,0:12:24.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mission complete. Returning to base.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.08,0:12:39.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,These are flowers called roses\Nthat bloom on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.79,0:12:42.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.50,0:12:47.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure that you want to fight\Nthis duel, Milord Slaine?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.42,0:12:51.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've fought for my life\Nmany times before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.13,0:12:52.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.13,0:12:55.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you worried about me,\NMiss Eddelrittuo?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.64,0:12:58.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You used to glare at me\Nall the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.77,0:13:01.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That was the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.69,0:13:06.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Roses signify many different things\Nin the language of flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.77,0:13:12.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Red roses mean "I love you,"\Nwhile blue roses mean "miracle."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.53,0:13:13.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Miracle...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.91,0:13:17.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But blue roses have\None other meaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.37,0:13:23.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That meaning...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.09,0:13:29.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...might be true.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.01,0:13:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's be off!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.01,0:13:34.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Herschel, launch!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.80,0:13:37.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Good hunting, Milord Slaine.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.39,0:13:40.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tharsis, launching.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.64,0:13:49.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The sight of a lowborn putting\Non airs is offensive to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.02,0:13:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,On the honor of Vers Orbital Knights,\NI shall exact punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.94,0:13:57.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Usurping an official post out\Nof self-interest without cause
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.03,0:13:59.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,disturbs both order\Nand public peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.66,0:14:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As the man in charge of Her Highness'\Nsafety, I will punish you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.21,0:14:10.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This will be a duel between\NCount Marylcian and Count Troyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.47,0:14:14.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.57,0:14:34.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're a slippery devil,\Njust as the rumors say.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.36,0:14:38.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But can you escape from\Nmy Herschel's attacks?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.18,0:15:02.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Milord Slaine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.35,0:15:07.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even with your predictions, not even\Nyou can cope with this many.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.07,0:15:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.86,0:15:21.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well, you're\Nfairly clever after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.74,0:15:22.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nevertheless!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.30,0:15:43.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Futile, futile, it is futile!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.52,0:15:53.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The flower language meaning\Nof blue roses is "miracle"...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.15,0:15:57.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But their other meaning
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.78,0:15:58.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,is "the impossible."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.66,0:16:05.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is it... is it truly hopeless?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.21,0:16:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Will she truly never\Nwake up again?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.38,0:16:20.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.89,0:16:24.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please give him a miracle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.06,0:16:31.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I see...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.27,0:16:34.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So it meant the impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.44,0:16:36.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I believe in you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.19,0:16:38.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There are no miracles!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.40,0:16:39.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Slaine!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.49,0:16:47.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is running all you can do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.33,0:16:49.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You inferior scum!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.52,0:17:20.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Inaho? What are you looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.15,0:17:22.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.57,0:17:23.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.70,0:17:27.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's nowhere left to run!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.83,0:17:32.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who has\Nnowhere to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.14,0:17:50.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Herschel's greatest weapon
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.06,0:17:52.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,is a simultaneous attack\Nfrom all directions.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.73,0:17:56.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But here, your attack is\Nconfined to just one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.99,0:18:08.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Material loading tunnels used during\Nthe moonbase's construction.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.45,0:18:09.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've been mapping them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.83,0:18:12.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be bested
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.00,0:18:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,by the likes of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.12,0:18:18.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think you are, Terran?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.64,0:18:34.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Victor...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.14,0:18:36.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...Count Troyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.65,0:18:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In accordance with the law,\Nall of Count Marylcian's assets
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.90,0:18:47.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,are to be transferred to Count\NSlaine Saazbaum Troyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.28,0:18:48.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you object?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.58,0:18:55.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As official witness, I, Barouhcruz,\Ncertify the outcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.83,0:19:00.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.75,0:19:04.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can see everything, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.46,0:19:05.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.38,0:19:12.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't see what\NI really want to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.64,0:19:20.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Inko, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.77,0:19:23.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want to get you involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.95,0:19:29.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jerk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.58,0:19:40.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In conclusion,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.79,0:19:46.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wish to inform you, the 37 Clans,\Nthe new policy that we shall adopt.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.12,0:19:50.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We, who have acquired new lands\Nand resources on Earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.55,0:19:54.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,do not need to rely on the\NVers homeworld forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.72,0:19:56.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Children eventually grow up
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.31,0:19:58.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and they must leave their\Nmothers' protection
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.14,0:20:01.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and strike out on their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.60,0:20:05.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I, Asseylum Vers Allusia,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.19,0:20:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,will take Count Slaine Saazbaum\NTroyard as my husband,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.40,0:20:16.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and proclaim that I shall create\Na new kingdom here in Earthspace.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.60,0:22:06.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I always admired you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.81,0:22:11.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You were beautiful, kindhearted,\Nand beloved by all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.82,0:22:14.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You had everything\Nthat I did not.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.87,0:22:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But you and I have one thing\Nin common, Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.83,0:22:28.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Royal blood. The Aldnoah activation factor.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.63,0:22:33.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It is a power that Slaine\Nhas need of now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.09,0:22:41.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have decided on Slaine.\NAnd Slaine has chosen me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.64,0:22:49.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,From now on,\NI am Asseylum Vers Allusia.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.48,0:22:52.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am you, Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.65,0:22:58.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you can let go, Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.50,0:23:12.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.01,0:23:18.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you are a puppet,\Nyou are still my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.72,0:23:25.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pleasant dreams.
